data.title: Winco CO-720 Double Hinged Waiter's Corkscrew
data.meta_description: Shop for the double hinged Winco waiter's corkscrew featuring an exceptionally durable design that will keep up with everyday use, at DISCOUNT prices. This corkscrew comes with a foil cutter and bottle cap opener to provide your wait staff with essential food service tools.
data.text:
Equip bartenders and waiters with the Winco CO-720 Double Hinged Waiter's Corkscrew. This functional corkscrew is perfect for opening bottles of bubbly champagne or fine wine and will help ensure that celebrations run smoothly.

This corkscrew is a great option for your food service establishment and includes other food service necessities such as a foil cutter and bottle cap opener. This double hinged waiter's corkscrew is perfect for your staff and will help your food service establishment maintain efficiency.

Stainless steel construction

Black finish

Double hinged design

Dimensions: 7.5" x 3.25"

WARNING: Attention CA residents: Cancer and Reproductive Harm --- www.P65Warnings.ca.gov.
